    "solution": "$\\begin{aligned} & \\tan 9^{\\circ}-\\tan 27^{\\circ}-\\tan 63^{\\circ}+\\tan 81^{\\circ} \\\\\\\\ & =\\tan 9^{\\circ}+\\tan \\left(90^{\\circ}-9^{\\circ}\\right)-\\tan 27^{\\circ}-\\tan \\left(90^{\\circ}-27^{\\circ}\\right) \\\\\\\\ & =\\tan 9^{\\circ}+\\cot 9^{\\circ}-\\tan 27^{\\circ}-\\cot 27^{\\circ} \\\\\\\\ & =\\frac{\\sin 9^{\\circ}}{\\cos 9^{\\circ}}+\\frac{\\cos 9^{\\circ}}{\\sin 9^{\\circ}}-\\left(\\frac{\\sin 27^{\\circ}}{\\cos 27^{\\circ}}+\\frac{\\cos 27^{\\circ}}{\\sin 27^{\\circ}}\\right) \\\\\\\\ & =\\frac{\\sin ^2 9^{\\circ}+\\cos ^2 9^{\\circ}}{\\sin 9^{\\circ} \\cos 9^{\\circ}}-\\left(\\frac{\\sin ^2 27^{\\circ}+\\cos ^2 27^{\\circ}}{\\cos 27^{\\circ} \\sin 27^{\\circ}}\\right) \\\\\\\\ & =\\frac{2}{\\sin 18^{\\circ}}-\\frac{2}{\\sin 54^{\\circ}} \\\\\\\\ & =\\frac{2 \\times 4}{\\sqrt{5}-1}-\\frac{2 \\times 4}{\\sqrt{5}+1} \\\\\\\\ & =8\\left(\\frac{\\sqrt{5}+1-\\sqrt{5}+1}{5-1}\\right)=2(2)=4\\end{aligned}$",
